---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="ADANI (APSEZ) Marine — Fuel Efficiency | Rentar"
  description="Commercial fleet validation of the Rentar Fuel Catalyst on ADANI (APSEZ) marine tugboats in Indian waters. Demonstrated meaningful fuel efficiency improvement."
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:45vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">Commercial Fleet Validation</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;">ADANI (APSEZ) Marine</h1>
      <p>Demonstrated fuel efficiency improvement on marine tugboats operating in Indian waters. Fuel flow meter measured, field validated.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="split-content">
          <p class="section-label">Case Study</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Measured fuel efficiency in marine operations</h2>
          <p class="section-text">The Rentar Fuel Catalyst was deployed on ADANI (APSEZ) marine tugboats operating in Indian waters. Fuel flow meters measured net fuel consumption on two tugboats with propulsion engines to quantify the fuel efficiency impact of the Rentar technology under commercial operating conditions.</p>
          <p class="section-text">Consistent fuel savings were demonstrated across marine vessels, validating the Rentar Fuel Catalyst's effectiveness in saltwater marine environments with continuous-duty propulsion engines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="split-image" style="background:transparent; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
          <iframe src="/images/marine_fuel_reduction" style="width:100%; max-width:960px; height:480px; border:0;" title="ADANI Marine Fuel Reduction Visualization" loading="lazy"></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Deployment Details</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Validation parameters</h2>
      <div class="val-specs" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); margin-bottom:32px;">
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Application</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">Marine Tugboats</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Measured Result</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">Meaningful</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Location</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">India</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-spec">
          <p class="val-spec-label">Status</p>
          <p class="val-spec-value">Demonstrated</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="val-ribbon" style="padding:0;">
        <span class="val-badge val-badge--active">Marine</span>
        <span class="val-badge val-badge--active">Field Validated</span>
        <span class="val-badge">Patent Protected</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label">Key Findings</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">What the deployment confirmed</h2>
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>Fuel flow meters measured net fuel consumption on two ADANI (APSEZ) tugboats before and after installation of the Rentar Fuel Catalyst. The metered data demonstrated meaningful fuel efficiency improvement across vessels operating in Indian waters.</p>
        <p class="manifesto-highlight">Consistent fuel savings demonstrated across marine vessels operating under commercial conditions in Indian waters.</p>
        <p>The deployment validated the Rentar Fuel Catalyst's performance in saltwater marine environments, where engine reliability and fuel efficiency are critical to operational economics. The passive in-line design proved well-suited to the continuous-duty propulsion cycles typical of harbor tug operations.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:40px; text-align:center;">
        <a href="/downloads/RENTAR-ADANI_Reference_Letter.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Download Reference Letter</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--navy); text-align:center;">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Next steps</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--white);">Evaluate the Rentar Fuel Catalyst for your marine fleet</h2>
      <p class="section-text" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom:40px;">Our team will work with your engineers to design a validation program for your specific vessel types, engine configurations, and operating profiles.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact sales</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
